# XIAOZHI agent data home (Cursor)

This project uses XIAOZHI with **isolated memory persistence** for Cursor:

- Default data root: `~/.cursor/xiaozhi` (not `~/.claude`)
- Env var: `XIAOZHI_AGENT_DATA_HOME` (set automatically by XIAOZHI's Cursor `sessionStart` hook when hooks are wired)
- Project override: `.cursor/xiaozhi-agent-data.json` → `agentDataHome`

If the user asks where XIAOZHI stored session context or learned skills, point them at `$XIAOZHI_AGENT_DATA_HOME/session-data/` and `$XIAOZHI_AGENT_DATA_HOME/skills/learned/`.

To **share** memory with Claude Code intentionally (not recommended for parallel use), set `XIAOZHI_AGENT_DATA_HOME` to `~/.claude` in the shell or in `.cursor/xiaozhi-agent-data.json`.
